### This repo consists of some ambiguous go mini projects

# What learnt

## 1. Project setup

```
 > -- Install go from go official website https://go.dev/dl/
 > -- Install a go extension for better developer experience https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=golang.Go
 > -- create main.go file
 > -- create project's module *go mod init <module path>*
```
